metadata.name: -PEPE FAMILY GRAIL-
metadata.description:
I am always amazed at the creation of all the Pepe Family artists. There are always crazy ideas every week.  
Each artist helps the others with their creativity by improving the world that Matt Furie has invented.

This NFT is a tribute to all the Artists who create every day on our favorite frog but also a tribute to the collectors who without them nothing would be possible.

Thanks to the Frog Fam artists who are in this work.

72 hours MINT.

Anyone who gets this NFT after 72 hours will receive an Airdrop on Friday November 4th (A 3D creation by me)

-50 Mint = new Airdrop  
-100 Mint = new Airdrop  
-1000 Mint = an Airdrop twice a month for 1 year
